1
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:33,760
Who is it?

2
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:45,330
Something happened in the warehouse.

3
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,640
Dad, you guys talk first.

4
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,360
What happened?

5
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:02,040
Someone broke into the warehouse at night.

6
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:03,240
Did you see who it was?

7
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:04,840
Our people found it in time.

8
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,640
But he reacted quickly and didn't stay.

9
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,560
He got away.

10
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,240
It's here! It's here! It's here!

11
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:11,900
It's the same as before. It's the same as before.

12
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,120
Isn’t this

13
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:28,120
I gave to Song Qingzhou?

14
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,759
Who sent you here?

15
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,000
Yes, sir.

16
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,280
What are you thinking about?

17
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,120
The soap of the Yao family

18
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,880
will be put into the market in a week.

19
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,740
When are you going to take action?

20
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,079
One week later.

21
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,520
The soap problem

22
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,760
will be exposed.

23
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,480
Let’s take action as soon as possible.

24
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,720
Song Huainan’s informant is staring at me.

25
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,450
We can’t let him find anything.

26
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,040
Master!

27
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,040
Help! Help!

28
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,160
Someone smashed our shop.

29
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,720
A group of people claimed that they used Yao's products.

30
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,960
and their faces are red and pimples.

31
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,360
There are so many of them.

32
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,160
How could this happen?

33
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,040
Master,

34
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,360
there's a new shop in South Street.

35
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,079
Their products can solve the problem of pimples.

36
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,640
All the customers went there.

37
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,560
Mr. Yiu.

38
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,920
How dare you lie to me with a fake?

39
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,160
Mr. Johnson.

40
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:57,400
How could I take a fake one?

41
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,680
This is the sample you gave me.

42
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:03,000
This is the product you're launching now.

43
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,920
I'll give you two choices now.

44
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,840
One, terminate the contract.

45
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,160
and compensate me for all my losses.

46
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,290
I choose number two.

47
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,200
Die!

48
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,880
Mr. Johnson.

49
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,280
Calm down.

50
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,640
You have to give me some time

51
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,840
so that I can know what's going on.

52
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,640
I'll give you three days

53
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,960
to collect all the compensation.

54
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,880
Otherwise, you will know.

55
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,360
What's going on?

56
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:36,200
Is there something wrong with the secret recipe you gave me?

57
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,800
How could there be a problem?

58
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:40,400
The foreigners are very satisfied with your sample.

59
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,240
Now you're bringing up the secret recipe.

60
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,840
What happened?

61
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,300
The secret recipe is fine.

62
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:49,200
Then I'll follow the product.

63
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,480
Why is there a problem?

64
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,680
That's what I wanted to ask you.

65
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,880
Mr Yao.

66
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,240
Don't you think you're the ones who cut the materials?

67
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,520
Stop talking nonsense.

68
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,480
I have faith in you.

69
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,920
Calm down.

70
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,760
Everyone will say it.

71
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,400
But what's the truth?

72
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,160
Who knows?

73
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:16,000
You suspect me and don't trust me.

74
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:19,800
I'm not interested in business.

75
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:22,360
But now you've caused me such a big trouble.

76
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,800
Not only did you offend the Westerners,

77
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,440
but also business matters.

78
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,040
The loss of our family

79
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,200
the Yao family's loss.

80
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,240
Take Mr Yao to withdraw money.

81
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,920
Yes.

82
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,680
What do you mean?

83
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,280
Let's go.

84
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,820
Son, you're finally here.

85
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,440
What are you doing? Let go of my father!

86
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,840
No one can disobey

87
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,159
No one can disobey it.

88
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,600
You’d better find your sister Sheng

89
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,080
to find a way.

90
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,210
I'll go find him.

91
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,240
Tell me.

92
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,840
Stop looking. Go.

93
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,720
Don’t delay the marshal.

94
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,080
Song Huainan, what do you mean?

95
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,200
Something happened to our Yao family.

96
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,520
You hit me when I'm down, right?

97
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,680
Yiu Li Fu, let's get to the point.

98
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,680
I've made it clear to your father.

99
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,880
Something is wrong with the products produced by the Yao family.

100
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,080
you should pay for it.

101
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,450
You're forcing my father to death.

102
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,480
You know

103
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,480
he loves money as much as his life.

104
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,200
Now the foreigners want to compensate us.

105
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,880
The Song family also wants us to compensate.

106
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:31,560
Do you want our family to go bankrupt?

107
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:34,520
It's normal to pay for the disaster.

108
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,760
Huainan.

109
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,120
I thought our relationship

110
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,720
you wouldn't go this far.

111
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,740
It seems I overestimated myself.

112
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,400
But Sheng is your wife.

113
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:52,600
Don't you care about her feelings at all?

114
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,680
I've already given the Yao family face.

115
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,720
Aren't you two living a good life?

116
00:05:57,360 --> 00:06:00,760
I advise you to think about what will happen to the Zhu family.

117
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,040
Guards!

118
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,200
Yes.

119
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:16,760
Young Master Yao

120
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,440
Go get Young Mistress

121
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,280
Young Master Yao

122
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:21,280
Young Mistress is not home today

123
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,570
Where did she go?

124
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,920
I don't know.

125
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:28,600
The Yao family won't be able to turn over this time.

126
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,520
Leave.

127
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,800
Are you looking for Sheng?

128
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,260
I need to see her urgently.

129
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:54,080
Dad, what's wrong?

130
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,800
Sheng.

131
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:03,680
Please help me.

132
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:07,400
Song Huainan is trying to kill me.

133
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:10,240
Since something happened to the soap factory,

134
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:13,320
he took all our Yao family's money.

135
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,080
Now the foreigners want me to claim compensation.

136
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:18,640
How can I compensate them?

137
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:28,800
My daughter.

138
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,520
Don't scare me.

139
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,159
I...

140
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,159
Daughter.

141
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,640
Yao Kunshu.

142
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:40,440
Open your eyes and see clearly.

143
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,440
I'm not Yao Sheng.

144
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,000
Do you remember me?

145
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,159
Daughter.

146
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,480
I'm Zhu Luoli.

147
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,800
The daughter of the Zhu family

148
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,800
and Song Huainan.

149
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,720
You...

150
00:07:57,040 --> 00:08:00,040
Yao Kunshu, go to hell!

151
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,600
Father!

152
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,080
Father!

153
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,360
I'm Lev.

154
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,900
Open your eyes and look at me, Father.

155
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,440
Who did it?

156
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:24,040
I was forced by Song Huainan.

157
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:32,640
Song Huainan, I won’t let you go.

158
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,799
I will make you pay.

159
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,400
Song Huainan.

160
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,720
You are the one who destroyed my family!

161
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,799
I want you to be isolated.

162
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,520
and die a horrible death.

163
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:49,360
Is there any misunderstanding?

164
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,400
Of course your family

165
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,960
speak for your family.

166
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,720
This is our family's matter.

167
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,200
You should go back first.

168
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,360
Commander, we've found the buyer

169
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,420
We have found the investor behind it.

170
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,000
Who is it?

171
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,040
It's a woman

172
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,080
But I've never seen her.

173
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,560
She's a middleman.

174
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,920
A woman?

175
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:22,880
How could a woman have the secret recipe of Zhu Family?

176
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,360
Have you found Zhu Luoli's body?

177
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,960
Not yet.

178
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,920
Commander, you mean

179
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:38,480
Investigate. No matter what it takes,

180
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,040
Yes.
